h2 Fieldset

p 
  | Wrapping your form content with a <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> tag allows you to 
  | group related elements inside of your form. Adding the <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> 
  | tag allows you to denote each section with a small heading.

