h2 Input Modifiers

p 
  | Modifier classes have been included that should help in appropriately styling 
  | inputs inside of your forms.

h3 Input Sizes

p
  | The modifier classes <code>.input--small</code> and <code>.input--large</code> 
  | can be used on <code>&lt;input&gt;</code> elements to adjust the size of the element.

